JsStaticEval
public static class JsStaticEval.FindBreakContinueStatementsVisitor
extends JsVisitor

Examines code to find out whether it contains any break or continue statements. TODO: We could be more sophisticated with this. A nested while loop with an unlabeled break should not cause this visitor to return false. Nor should a labeled break break to another context.
